+            access to a coworking space, received unemployment benefits, and
+            cleared the bandwidth to launch my own startup. For the first time
+            in <mark style="background-color: #e0e0e0">15 years</mark>, I was
+            not consumed by survival. I had one year, a desk, and the breathing
+            room to <u>work toward independence</u>.
+          </p>
