-        <h1>Response Rights & Legal Integrity</h1>
-
-        <h2>🛡️ Purpose</h2>
-        <p>
-          This page outlines the public policy for legal interactions, factual
-          rebuttals, correction requests, and the documentation of any attempts
-          to suppress or informally negotiate away public interest material.
-        </p>
-
-        <h2>📣 Right of Reply</h2>
-        <ul>
-          <li>Submit a verifiable factual correction</li>
-          <li>Provide context or supporting documents</li>
-          <li>Request anonymization (if justified and proportionate)</li>
-        </ul>
-        <p>
-          Requests will be reviewed in good faith. Valid additions or
-          clarifications will be acknowledged and publicly reflected in
-          footnotes or appendices.
-        </p>
-
-        <h2>☎️ Recording Policy for Calls & Outreach</h2>
-        <p>
-          Due to past experiences of coercion and veiled threats, all phone
-          calls and voice messages <strong>may be recorded</strong> for
-          transparency, archiving, and legal protection.
-        </p>
-        <ul>
-          <li>
-            This includes direct calls, intermediaries, and informal emissaries.
-          </li>
-          <li>
-            Any interaction deemed intimidatory, manipulative, or designed to
-            bypass formal channels
-            <strong>may be documented and referenced</strong> in future updates.
-          </li>
-        </ul>
-
-        <h2>📨 Handling Legal Letters or Notices</h2>
-        <ul>
-          <li>
-            Legal communication may be summarized, quoted, or published in full.
-          </li>
-          <li>
-            Identities may be anonymized unless public or legally relevant.
-          </li>
-          <li>
-            Communications relying on intimidation may be publicly challenged.
-          </li>
-        </ul>
-
-        <h2>🔍 Transparency Clause</h2>
-        <p>This project maintains the right to:</p>
-        <ul>
-          <li>Publicly respond to formal or informal pressure</li>
-          <li>Trace outreach patterns and motives</li>
-          <li>Document attempts to distort or silence structural critique</li>
-        </ul>
-        <blockquote>
-          This archive is not a negotiation table — it is a civic documentation
-          platform.
-        </blockquote>
-
-        <h2>📬 Contact Protocol</h2>
-        <p>For rebuttals or formal communication:</p>
-        <ul>
